</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Changing_User_Account_Names"> Changing User Account Names </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Removing_User_Accounts"> Removing User Accounts </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Configuring_User_Registration"> Configuring User Registration </a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Verification_of_the_new_registration_email_address"> Verification of the new registration email address </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Administrative_approval_of_new_registrations"> Administrative approval of new registrations </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Registration_Email_Requirements"> Registration Email Requirements </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Expiration_of_pending_registrations_and_approvals"> Expiration of pending registrations and approvals </a>
